rmal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7fd67d18f55fc19979567d6566a3cd89d585b5e","tid":463220,"uid":126973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T20:52:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Mill唔係有theory of computation解答左咩fictional characters咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n得返一小時due<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢當 fictional name 係 empty term<br />\n<br />\nThe following sentence is true:  <br />\n<br />\nJames Bond is disgustingly successful.  <br />\n<br />\nBut on Mill'saccount it couldn't be, because the subject term does<br />\nnot denote.  So it would be meaningless, and that would make the sentence also<br />\nmeaningless, not true.  And don't try to tell us it refers to a) a fictional<br />\ncharacter, which gives up all sense of reality or pretense to being scientific,  or<br />\nb) an idea (an idea isn't the referent in &quot;Reagan is wrinkled&quot;, so it shouldn't be <br />\nthe referent here).<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.d.umn.edu/~dcole/millname.txt\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.d.umn.edu%2F~dcole%2Fmillname.txt&d=qFMizAWkK58qCn8pkwBdHW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=32badf03\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.d.umn.edu/~dcole/millname.txt</a>"},{"pid":"fa4002683d4a1964db29725bbb79be1a12d4893c","tid":463220,"uid":126973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T20:57:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Mill唔係有theory of computation解答左咩fictional characters咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n得返一小時due<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nWhat's the problem of that theory after theory of connotation<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔明問緊咩 theory <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 算啦 已經太遲 <br />\n下次早d"}]}